Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.01,0:00:02.96,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:07.62,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是宇宙大爆炸後產生宇宙時就存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.39,0:00:09.54,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,古往今來的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:15.40,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,從多數卡片中選擇了40枚組合起來構築了屬於自己的卡組
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:17.79,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,進行了激烈的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:19.45,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,於是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:22.64,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,長久以來站在戰爭歷史巔峰造極的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:25.29,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這究極的最強的卡片遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:27.29,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,「戰鬥生物」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:29.35,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,美國大選也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:31.11,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,人氣偶像解散也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:33.52,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 動畫軟體的出貨量也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:36.80,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,都是由這個「戰鬥生物」的勝負來決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:38.01,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.38,0:00:41.93,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,得「戰鬥生物」者得天下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.72,0:00:45.59,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 全國的「戰鬥生物」者們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:48.30,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在拿起卡組站起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.41,0:00:52.67,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 投入卡片戰爭的洶湧海濤之中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.76,0:01:04.15,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:11.61,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,咳咳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.06,0:01:13.55,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼現在就是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.03,0:01:16.17,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,超人氣卡片遊戲 「戰鬥生物」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.64,0:01:18.20,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,通稱「戰生」的新卡包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.40,0:01:21.70,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,Evolution of Nerd的開包儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.63,0:01:25.91,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 先打開第一包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:30.43,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有稀有卡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.67,0:01:32.82,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且生物全是香草
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:35.24,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這個作為開頭很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:37.39,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來要上咯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:40.15,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那究竟有沒有稀有卡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:42.89,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦… 沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:44.49,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:48.06,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因為沒那麼容易出才是稀有卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:56.54,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有…沒有…沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:08.18,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是最後一包了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:20.13,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:25.43,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到能看到那動畫的禁放集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:29.32,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能小看重播呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.07,0:02:32.40,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.64,0:02:35.77,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 是這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.72,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然這麼徹底地全部踩雷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:43.20,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定是被卡片的女神拋棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:45.60,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:49.60,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 這個還沒開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:54.21,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這個是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:57.07,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,魔術卡 30年的家裡蹲！
