Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:22.88,akiba-op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}基因裡薪火相傳的 時代劇 戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:25.70,akiba-op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}從遙遠的地方就開始襲來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:28.64,akiba-op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想堂堂正正地面對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:30.98,akiba-op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}歡迎  與我握手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:33.88,akiba-op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但又並非所有人都厭惡犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:37.29,akiba-op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}將黑暗喀嚓喀嚓地割裂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:40.35,akiba-op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}剪刀石頭布 轉向那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:45.86,akiba-op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今宵宵宵 OUT ？ SAFE ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:51.60,akiba-op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}盡情跳舞 嬉鬧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:54.35,akiba-op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大家也 一起
